metadata.description: The Season 1 poster for the first ever web3 animated series. DeadHeads Season 1 follows the story of Damien, a lost soul who dies and finds himself in the mysterious Underworld. In his search for a way out, Damien for the first time finds self-purpose. 'It wasn't until I died, that I found a reason to live.'
metadata.name: DeadHeads Season 1 Poster: Golden Edition
